{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act4d0_level_act4d0_st04","storyGroup":"act4d0","storySort":4,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"","storyName":"存续公正","storyPic":"storyMainPic_level_act4d0_st04","storyInfo":"拉特兰公证所派出执行者送葬人，前往叙拉古执行委托。\n送葬人找到了委托目标红云，遵循委托，他将带其前往罗德岛接受治疗。\n","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"activities/act4d0/level_act4d0_st04","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"USE_ITEM","costItemType":"MATERIAL","costItemId":"STORY_REVIEW_COIN","costItemCount":1,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":[],"prev":2,"next":4,"characters":["红云","？？？","送葬人","老猎人"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"第一关（前）","id":0},{"type":"Dialog","id":1},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":2},{"type":"Text","text":"♪你是否听闻一声惊雷？","id":3},{"type":"Text","text":"♪雨成帘，不见山","id":4},{"type":"Text","text":"♪我早已忘记是何人何物","id":5},{"type":"Text","text":"♪将我引领入此道","id":6},{"type":"Text","text":"♪远方的红色的云啊","id":7},{"type":"Text","text":"♪带我回到故乡","id":8},{"type":"Dialog","id":9},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":10},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$mist_intro","key":"$mist_loop","volume":"0.6","crossfade":"1","id":11,"musicid":0},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_towerinside","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":12},{"type":"Text","text":"10:37 A.M.    天气/多云","id":13},{"type":"Text","text":"叙拉古天灾低发区，荒野，某林中小屋","id":14},{"type":"Dialog","id":15},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":16},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":17},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"唔......？","id":18,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"......","id":19,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_279_excu_4#6","id":20},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我已经听见了歌声，躲藏是不必要的，我没有恶意。","id":21,"figure":"char_279_excu_4#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","id":22},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"......每个刽子手都是这么说的。但最后，总是见血。","id":23,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_279_excu_4#6","id":24},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"刽子手？我不明白你的用词。我是拉特兰公证所——","id":25,"figure":"char_279_excu_4#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","id":26},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"闭嘴！你骗不了我！","id":27,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Dialog","id":28},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":29},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_atk_arrow_h","id":30},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":31},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":32},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_atk_arrow_h","id":33},{"type":"Delay","time":"1.5","id":34},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"得手了！","id":35,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Dialog","id":36},{"type":"Character","id":37},{"type":"Character","name":"char_279_excu_4#6","id":38},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"并没有。","id":39,"figure":"char_279_excu_4#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","id":40},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"咦？！","id":41,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_279_excu_4#6","id":42},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"失礼了。","id":43,"figure":"char_279_excu_4#6"},{"type":"Dialog","id":44},{"type":"Character","id":45},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":46},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":47},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$char_emp","volume":"0.9","id":48},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":49},{"type":"Character","name":"char_279_excu_4","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":50},{"type":"Delay","time":"3","id":51},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"目标翻窗逃走，反应相当迅速。","id":52,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"环境确认。腌制的羽兽肉，鞣制用的架子，处理过的牙兽皮，手工小刀和木质工具。","id":53,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"放下弓。我清楚你的位置，你埋伏在窗后。","id":54,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"重申一遍，我对你没有恶意。","id":55,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","id":56},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"——不行！","id":57,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Dialog","id":58},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":59},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_atk_arrow_h","id":60},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":61},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":62},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_atk_arrow_h","id":63},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":64},{"type":"Character","name":"char_279_excu_4","id":65},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你的警戒心很强。","id":66,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","id":67},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"尝尝这一箭！","id":68,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Dialog","id":69},{"type":"Character","name":"char_279_excu_4","id":70},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":71},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_atk_arrow_h","id":72},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":73},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","id":74},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"抓，用手抓住了箭身？","id":75,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"怎么会......你究竟是什么人！","id":76,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Dialog","id":77},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":78},{"type":"Character","name":"char_279_excu_4","id":79},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"诚如报告所说，遗嘱继承人暴躁排外，难以交流。","id":80,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Dialog","id":81},{"type":"Character","id":82},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":83},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":84},{"type":"Character","id":85},{"type":"Background","id":86},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":87},{"type":"Character","name":"char_279_excu_4","id":88},{"type":"Text","text":"以上就是本人遗嘱的全部内容。","id":89},{"type":"Text","text":"除此之外，我有一条出于私心的请求。","id":90},{"type":"Text","text":"在叙拉古的森林之中，我遇到了一位独臂的沃尔珀少女。","id":91},{"type":"Text","text":"她沉溺在对过去的复仇之中，拘泥于那片染血的土地。","id":92},{"type":"Text","text":"出于怜悯，我帮助了她，也许这伤害到了她的自尊，但她倔强的求生方式的确感动了我。","id":93},{"type":"Text","text":"后来我意识到，我一时兴起的援助，不过是坚定了她复仇的执念，这让我寝食难安。","id":94},{"type":"Text","text":"所以我想把我的一切赠送给她，尽管我几乎一无所有，只剩那么点可悲的遗物。","id":95},{"type":"Text","text":"——恕我打断一下，您的亲属列表里没有沃尔珀人。这会为我们的工作带来很多麻烦。","id":96},{"type":"Text","text":"所以，这只是一位膝下无子的拉特兰公民，在将死之际向公证所提出的小小请求。","id":97},{"type":"Dialog","id":98},{"type":"Character","id":99},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":100},{"type":"Character","id":101},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$m_dia_street_intro","key":"$m_dia_street_loop","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1.5","id":102,"musicid":1},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_forest","screenadapt":"coverall","id":103},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":104},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","id":105},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"......","id":106,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"（他的身上，有血的气味，而且，有股讨厌的感觉......）","id":107,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"（又是来破坏我们家园的人吗，讨厌，好讨厌！）","id":108,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Dialog","id":109},{"type":"Character","id":110},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":111},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":112},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","id":113},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"上钩了！","id":114,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_279_excu_4","id":115},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"原来如此，又是个陷阱。似乎各个方位都有触发机关。","id":116,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":117},{"type":"Dialog","id":118},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","id":119},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"听着！你已经走进了猎人的陷阱，不想死的话，就把你的武器放下，一步也不要动！","id":120,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":121},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"如果能方便交流，可以。","id":122,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":123},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"你是什么人？","id":124,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":125},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"拉特兰公证所的执行者，本次的遗嘱执行人。可以称呼我“送葬人”。","id":126,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":127},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"拉特兰......？","id":128,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":129},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"“红云”，你是被委托的对象。","id":130,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":131},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"你为什么会知道我的名字？","id":132,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":133},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"你的名字由遗嘱人迪伦马特先生告知。","id":134,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":135},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"我不认识这个人。","id":136,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":137},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"出于某些原因，他曾使用多个化名。","id":138,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":139},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"你要带我去哪里？","id":140,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":141},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"出于保密要求，我不能说。","id":142,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":143},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"......嘁，满嘴谎话！你就死在这里吧！","id":144,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"我是不会离开这儿的，我的爸爸妈妈，叔叔阿姨，还有朋友，我的族人，都，都......","id":145,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":146},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"我的任务只是带你离开。","id":147,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":148},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"不要再说胡话了！你知道自己的处境吗！","id":149,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":150},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"我处在无法进行交涉的情况下。","id":151,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":152},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"哼，走进这片森林的，都只会是我们的猎物。","id":153,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"你的脚下的骨头，原本都是些野兽和坏人！","id":154,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":155},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"理解。据点周围布满陷阱。","id":156,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"落穴，绊索，土制地雷，自动飞镖。","id":157,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"请放心，我已经全部解除了。陷阱很初级，有伤到委托对象你的可能性。","id":158,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":159},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"......","id":160,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":161},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"请跟我走。","id":162,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":163},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"——！走开！","id":164,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"再往前一步，我就射穿你！","id":165,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","id":166},{"type":"playsound","key":"$leaveshake","volume":"0.7","id":167},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":168},{"type":"Character","name":"char_279_excu_4","id":169},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"又逃了。","id":170,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Dialog","id":171},{"type":"Character","id":172},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":173},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":174},{"type":"Character","id":175},{"type":"Background","id":176},{"type":"cameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"1","fadetime":"0","id":177},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":178},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":179},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":180},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"喂，你为什么要救我？","id":181,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","id":182},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老猎人","text":"毕竟我也是个猎人。","id":183},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老猎人","text":"看到一位可敬的同行失去了一只臂膀，血肉模糊地躺在一只牙兽的身边，我怎么能视而不见呢？","id":184},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","id":185},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"哼......你根本不是猎人，你骗不了我。你身上没有泥土的味道。","id":186,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","id":187},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老猎人","text":"哈哈，瞒不过你，但亲眼目睹那副景象的时候，我被年幼却征服了荒野的你感动了，这是实话。","id":188},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","id":189},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"那是什么意思？","id":190,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","id":191},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老猎人","text":"只是我的自言自语。","id":192},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","id":193},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"你脑袋上的那个圆，还有背后的装饰，是怎么回事？","id":194,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","id":195},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老猎人","text":"小家伙，你没见过拉特兰人吗？","id":196},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","id":197},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"嗯。","id":198,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","id":199},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老猎人","text":"这是......我抛却的故土给我留下的印记。","id":200},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","id":201},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"人是没法抛弃家的泥土的。","id":202,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","id":203},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老猎人","text":"也许吧，总之，发生了很多事，来，试着站起身来吧。","id":204},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老猎人","text":"让我来帮你装上这个。","id":205},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","id":206},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"这是......？胳膊？铁做的胳膊？好奇怪的东西。","id":207,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","id":208},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老猎人","text":"代表我对一位荒野之子的敬意。","id":209},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","id":210},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"你是个修东西的？","id":211,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","id":212},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老猎人","text":"很久以前的职责让我学会了很多东西。","id":213},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","id":214},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"......","id":215,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"......你救过我，你不是个坏人。为了报仇，我很需要一只胳膊，谢谢。","id":216,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","id":217},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老猎人","text":"复仇吗......我不会指点你的命运。","id":218},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老猎人","text":"但当你用这只手臂拉动弓弦的时候，你可以想想，除了报仇以外，我们是为什么活着。","id":219},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老猎人","text":"想得少了，就会沦落到我今天这样。","id":220},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","id":221},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"我——","id":222,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","id":223},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老猎人","text":"不要说什么“为了复仇而活”，这太老套了，很没意思的。","id":224},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老猎人","text":"......没错，很没意思的。","id":225},{"type":"Dialog","id":226},{"type":"Character","id":227},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":228},{"type":"Character","id":229},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$m_dia_street_intro","key":"$m_dia_street_loop","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1.5","id":230,"musicid":2},{"type":"cameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0","fadetime":"0","id":231},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_forest","screenadapt":"coverall","id":232},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":233},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","id":234},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"（拉特兰......他说他是拉特兰人......）","id":235,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"（难道他真的是......)","id":236,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":237},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"唔！又来，好痛！","id":238,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4#3","focus":"2","id":239},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"看来迪伦马特先生的判断是正确的。","id":240,"figure":"char_279_excu_4#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4#3","focus":"1","id":241},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"什么？","id":242,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"可恶，你是什么时候追到这里的？","id":243,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":244},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"唔！放开我！！","id":245,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":246},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"停手吧，既然你是遗嘱继承人，我就不能伤害你。","id":247,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"这是他的信。","id":248,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","id":249},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"——！！","id":250,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Dialog","id":251},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":252},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_atk_arrow_h","id":253},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":254},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":255},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_atk_arrow_h","id":256},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":257},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":258},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"为什么还要抵抗？","id":259,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":260},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"......信上有他的气味，血的气味，你对他做了什么！？","id":261,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":262},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"从拉特兰抵达这里的旅程非常漫长，气味分子不可能有所保留。","id":263,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":264},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"回答我！否则你会死在这里！","id":265,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Dialog","id":266},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","id":267},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":268},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"呃！","id":269,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":270},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"首先，我认为展示力量差距有助于对话成立。","id":271,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"其次，出于对遗嘱继承人的尊重，我可以回答你。","id":272,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"迪伦马特先生死在手术台上，并不安详。他身患一种无法治愈的疾病。","id":273,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":274},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"你——！松手！","id":275,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":276},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"这是他的选择。","id":277,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":278},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"喂！你，你在干嘛！","id":279,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":280},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":281},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"源石已经破体而出，感染程度在加剧。","id":282,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":283},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"这不关你事！","id":284,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":285},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"如果执行对象坚持拒绝，原则上，我可以放弃。","id":286,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"但委托人和上司给予了我一个附属条约，我必须执行。","id":287,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":288},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"——你到底要怎么样？","id":289,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":290},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"“让红云活下去”。","id":291,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"但因为要求笼统，所以实行起来很复杂，希望你能配合。","id":292,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":293},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"......这也是那个人的委托？","id":294,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":295},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"是的。他变卖了所有的财产，支付了包括公证所的额外手续费，以及你将来的治疗开销。","id":296,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":297},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"可是，为什么？他只是路过这片森林......","id":298,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":299},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"他想让你活下去。","id":300,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":301},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"所以我问为什么！","id":302,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":303},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"因为他觉得你值得活下去。","id":304,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"既然遗嘱已经传达到位，我的工作就告一段落了。","id":305,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":306},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"什......！你什么时候塞给我的——！","id":307,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":308},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"在下一步行动前，我必须听到你的答复。","id":309,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"“你想活下去吗？”","id":310,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":311},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"......","id":312,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":313},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"你只要回答，想，或是不想。","id":314,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"我们的时间不多。","id":315,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":316},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"我——","id":317,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Dialog","id":318},{"type":"Character","id":319},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":320},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":321},{"type":"Character","id":322},{"type":"Background","id":323},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":324},{"type":"Text","text":"对了，先生，我该怎么称呼你？","id":325},{"type":"Text","text":"——送葬人。如果你执意要称呼我的话。","id":326},{"type":"Text","text":"非常感谢你愿意接受我的委托。","id":327},{"type":"Text","text":"——是中庭公证所做出了决定，我只是履行职责。","id":328},{"type":"Text","text":"哈哈，也是。在你寻找红云的过程中，我还有一个小小的请求。","id":329},{"type":"Text","text":"——视情况，我可能会拒绝你的口头诉求。希望你以纸面申请的形式递交公证所。","id":330},{"type":"Text","text":"先生可真是不留情面，没关系，只是一个小小的要求。","id":331},{"type":"Text","text":"不要告诉她关于我的过去，随便编个借口吧，比如，我死在了手术台上？","id":332},{"type":"Text","text":"——我不明白这其中的必要性，这也不符合你的身份。你逃避公证所多年，而且你枪杀了......","id":333},{"type":"Text","text":"打住。如果我说，这能为你的工作省去很多麻烦呢？","id":334},{"type":"Text","text":"——如果我判断的确如此的话，我会考虑尝试。","id":335},{"type":"Dialog","id":336},{"type":"Character","id":337},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":338},{"type":"Character","id":339},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$m_dia_street_intro","key":"$m_dia_street_loop","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1.5","id":340,"musicid":3},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_towerinside","screenadapt":"coverall","id":341},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":342},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":343},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"......所以，那个叫罗德岛的地方，真的能治疗这种奇怪的病？","id":344,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4#5","focus":"2","id":345},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"没有人能够抵抗矿石病。但也许可以缓解痛苦。","id":346,"figure":"char_279_excu_4#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"考虑到你先前对那些乌萨斯人所做的一切，我不建议你单独行动。","id":347,"figure":"char_279_excu_4#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"而我正好要去罗德岛履行另一份协议。","id":348,"figure":"char_279_excu_4#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4#5","focus":"1","id":349},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"你是在邀请我和你同行？","id":350,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":351},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"我认为这十分合理。","id":352,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":353},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"哼，我拒绝。","id":354,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"我还有很多事情要做，在离开这片土地之前，我要与族人们道别。","id":355,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":356},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"这里很危险，仇恨并不会因为一方的妥协而终结。","id":357,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":358},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"哼......你知道得很清楚。","id":359,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"无论你怎么说，别妨碍我。等到一切结束，我会去那个......罗德岛的，这样就行了吧？","id":360,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":361},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"我在考虑。","id":362,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":363},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"什么？","id":364,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":365},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"考虑如果那些亡命之徒再次找到你，我的子弹储备是否充足。","id":366,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":367},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"子弹......？不，你的意思是要陪着我回到荒漠！？","id":368,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":369},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"根据你的回答，你已被公证所视作接受遗嘱。","id":370,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"但遗嘱内容尚未履行完成，我不能放任你就这么暴露在危险中。这是我的义务。","id":371,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":372},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"我不需要你的帮助！我一直都是一个人——","id":373,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":374},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"以及，我认为你有故意妥协，然后趁机逃走的可能。","id":375,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":376},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"啧。","id":377,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":378},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"那么事不宜迟，我们出发吧。","id":379,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":380},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"喂！我没有答应你！我不需要你这种外人来......等等，你要去哪儿？你怎么知道那个方向的！？","id":381,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":382},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"调查的结果。","id":383,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":384},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"你脚下有——","id":385,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"2","id":386},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"送葬人","text":"我已经解除了陷阱，请跟上。","id":387,"figure":"char_279_excu_4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_190_clour","name2":"char_279_excu_4","focus":"1","id":388},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"红云","text":"啊啊——你这个怪人，我迟早要让你好看——！","id":389,"figure":"char_190_clour"},{"type":"Dialog","id":390},{"type":"Character","id":391},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":392},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":393},{"type":"Character","id":394},{"type":"Background","id":395},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":396},{"type":"Text","text":"请一定要照顾好她，送葬人先生。当然，也许对你而言也是一件好事。","id":397},{"type":"Text","text":"别摆出一副不理解的表情，你会明白的。","id":398},{"type":"Text","text":"希望你们能让她脱离泥泞。别让她像我一样。","id":399},{"type":"Text","text":"正义？也许我的所作所为是有正当性的吧，先生，如果公证所能够谅解我的话。","id":400},{"type":"Text","text":"但那依旧不是什么值得称赞的事情，相反，正因如此，才让人生显得荒谬之极。","id":401},{"type":"Text","text":"但她是我的遗产。","id":402},{"type":"Text","text":"是我的希望。","id":403},{"type":"Text","text":"愿主保佑。","id":404},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":405},{"type":"Dialog","id":406},{"type":"Blocker","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":407},{"type":"Image","id":408}],"characters":["红云","？？？","送葬人","老猎人"]}